# Comic Book Blog Application

 A modern blog application for comic book enthusiasts featuring posts about DC Comics and Marvel content. Built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

## Features

**Dynamic Posts**: View and manage comic book blog posts
 **Image Support**: Each post can include a featured image
 **CRUD Operations**:
  - Create new posts
  - Read post details
  - Update existing posts
  - Delete posts
 **Responsive Design**: Works on all device sizes
 **Comic-Inspired UI**: Stylish comic book aesthetic

## Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3 (Flexbox, Grid, Animations)
- JavaScript (ES6)
- [Font Awesome](https://fontawesome.com/) (for icons)
- Google Fonts (Pacifico, Bangers)

## Installation

1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/comic-blog-app.git
   comic-blog-app/
├── index.html        # Main HTML file
├── style.css         # Stylesheet
├── script.js         # JavaScript functionality
├── images/           # Image assets
└── README.md         # This file
Usage
Add a New Post:

Fill out the form with title, author, image URL, and content
Click "Submit"
View Post Details:

Click on any post title in the list
Edit a Post:

Click "Edit" on the post detail view
Modify the fields in the form
Click "Update"
Delete a Post:

Click "Delete" on the post detail view
Customization
Easily customize the blog by editing these variables in script.js:

